  <oversight_info>
    <is_fda_regulated_drug>Yes</is_fda_regulated_drug>
    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to test if VC-02™ combination product can be implanted
      subcutaneously in subjects with Type 1 Diabetes and Hypoglycemia Unawareness and maintained
      safely for up to two years. It will also test if VC-02 is an effective treatment for these
      subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
